Gabriella Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabriella_Wright 0 Gabriella Wright (born 19 June 1982) is an English-French actress and model, best known for playing Queen Claude of France in the series The Tudors and Viola in the film The Perfect Husband. She recently played a significant role as Gina in the action thriller The Transporter Refueled.
